title: FBI director confirming inquiry into Clinton email setup
text:
> Political FBI director confirming inquiry into Clinton email setup FILE - In this July 8, 2015 file photo, FBI Director James Comey testifies on Capitol Hill in Washington. Comey is confirming that the FBI is looking into the security of the setup of Hillary Rodham Clinton's email. But he's not answering questions about the investigation.
